      .s2-wrapper
        section.section2
          .section2__text
            p
              span.bold-text Purpose PlatinumTrade -
              |
              | is to give traders infinite opportunities, to be successful and financially independent person, without creating any obstacles and restrictions.

            p
              span.bold-text Mission PlatinumTrade -
              |
              | is to provide you, as a trader, the safest, most convenient and generally the best way to trade. Our pricing and execution modules guarantee the use of the most advanced and advanced technologies. Thanks to our partnership with the Reuters news provider, we receive real-time streams of accurate data, and our terms and conditions clearly indicate the difference between the market price in real time and the price of options. We provide expiration schedules at any given moment to ensure the calmness of the trader, so that the trader does not have any problematic issues.

            p Stability is of paramount importance for our company. We make every effort to ensure uninterrupted services, safe and simple trading, financial viability and strict compliance with the law.

            p We hope that your relationship with PlatinumTrade will be long-term, and we will do our best to make it profitable!
          .section2__logo: img(src="assets/img/logo.png", alt="logo.png")

      // /SECTION 2

