      .s3-wrapper
        section.section3
          h1.section3__header
            |  JOIN THE
            br
            span.bold-text PLATINUMTRADE.ORG
            br
            | AND TRADE
            br
            | AS A PROFESSIONAL!
          h5.section3__subheader PlatinumTrade Platform Advantages:
          ol.section3__list
            li Web interface, no need to download
            li Simple trade - easy to understand with clear explanations
            li Diverse products
            li User-friendly trade
            li Safe - the risk / profit ratio is clearly stated in the option
            li Quick and easy deposits in BTC
            li Constant development of highly profitable feeds in modern conditions.
          p.section3__text PlatinumTrade is committed to providing the most high-quality and unique trading platform that can be used by private investors around the world. Employees of GoldbergTrade are ready to provide traders with the necessary assistance, and professional brokers provide traders with guidance at every stage of the journey.
          p.section3__text
            span.bold-text PLATINUMTRADE.ORG -
            |  This is the leading platform for trading binary options to date. Now that binary options have become more popular than ever, PlatinumTrade provides traders with excellent working conditions in terms of security, availability of various functions, ease of use, provision of tools and training.
          p.section3__text Customer funds are stored on a separate account. Cash is only used to trade options through our website on behalf of the client and is never used for any other purpose. The management of our obligations and risks is carried out by professionals, and we guarantee the payment of your profit according to our conditions.
          p.section3__text In PlatinumTrade Company and in partner organizations there are professional forex brokers experts in the field of derivative financial instruments and risk management. In addition, we cooperate with payment systems. We deal with all aspects of trading binary options, so that you get the best impression of trading at any one time.


